description: A user created a new user account. Attackers can create new accounts to maintain their foothold on a system. Investigate the active user and newly created account.
A process appears to be abusing Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI). Some malware exploits WMI to perform malicious activities. Investigate the process tree.
cmdline: cmd.exe /Q /c net user /add plumber password /domain && net group "Domain Admins" plumber /add /domain 1> \Windows\Temp\bvmXOY 2>&1
